author: Paul Cullen
title: Coronavirus: Up to 400 people on waiting list for call confirming diagnosis
description: Contact tracing cannot begin until initial call is made
content:
Large numbers of people who have tested positive for Covid-19 have yet to receive a call confirming the diagnosis which would set in train efforts to trace their contacts.
